<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css">
</head>
<body class="portfolio-body auth-body">
    <div class="auth-shell">
        <div class="auth-card">
            <p class="eyebrow">포트폴리오 전시</p>
            <h1 class="auth-title">Portfo()io</h1>
            <p class="auth-subtitle">이메일과 비밀번호를 입력해 주세요.</p>
            <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                <div class="error-message"><%= error %></div>
            <% } %>
            <form action="/login" method="POST" class="auth-form">
                <label for="email" class="input-label">이메일</label>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
                </div>
                <label for="password" class="input-label">비밀번호</label>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="primary-button">로그인</button>
            </form>
            <div class="auth-footer">
                <p>계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/signup">가입하기</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
